---
import Prose from "@components/Prose.astro";
import BaseLayout from "@layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout pageTitle="Now | Hyun Don Moon">
  <Prose>
    <h1>Now</h1>

    <p>
      This page is inspired by Derek Sivers' <a
        href="https://nownownow.com/about"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer">/now pages</a
      > movement. It's a simple concept: a page that tells you what someone is focused
      on at this point in their life.
    </p>

    <section>
      <h3>November, 2024</h3>

      <ul>
        <li>
          <p>
            <strong>Work</strong>: Actively looking for frontend or software development roles. I have experience in Angular, TypeScript, React, and RxJS, and I'm open to remote or in-office positions, whether in Korea or internationally.
          </p>
        </li>

        <li>
          <p>
            <strong>Projects</strong>: Revisiting my <a href="https://ziplink.at/" target="_blank">Ziplink</a> project to add new quality-of-life features and looking for areas to improve overall functionality.
          </p>
        </li>

        <li>
          <p>
            <strong>Studying</strong>: Focusing solely on React this month. I'm reading <em>모던 리액트 Deep Dive</em> and exploring React source code to understand its inner workings. I'm also checking out libraries commonly used in the React ecosystem, like React Router and React Query, to expand my skill set.
          </p>
        </li>

        <li>
          <p>
            <strong>Reading</strong>: Currently reading The <em>Pragmatic Programmer</em> and <em>Essentialism: The Disciplined Pursuit of Less</em>.
          </p>
        </li>

        <li>
          <p>
            <strong>Learning</strong>: Finally starting driving lessons after putting it off for a long time.
          </p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </Prose>
</BaseLayout>
